Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:04.19,Cap,,0,0,0,,Unemployment is low by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:05.33,Cap,,0,0,0,,historic standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:07.31,Cap,,0,0,0,,So why are so many project
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:08.33,Cap,,0,0,0,,managers and analysts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:09.23,Cap,,0,0,0,,sending out hundreds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:10.25,Cap,,0,0,0,,of applications and hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.27,0:00:11.49,Cap,,0,0,0,,nothing back these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:12.98,Cap,,0,0,0,,The truth is, the market's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:13.46,Cap,,0,0,0,,changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:15.17,Cap,,0,0,0,,AI is reshaping how employers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:16.59,Cap,,0,0,0,,screen and select candidates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:18.14,Cap,,0,0,0,,and applications that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.49,Cap,,0,0,0,,reflect true authenticity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:20.69,Cap,,0,0,0,,are outperforming cold
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:21.72,Cap,,0,0,0,,applications.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:23.87,Cap,,0,0,0,,Join us at a free PMI
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:24.84,Cap,,0,0,0,,South Florida Lunch and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:25.91,Cap,,0,0,0,,Learn on Wednesday, July
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:27.80,Cap,,0,0,0,,29th, at noon, where
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:28.64,Cap,,0,0,0,,you'll learn more about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.66,0:00:29.78,Cap,,0,0,0,,the job search tactics
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:30.86,Cap,,0,0,0,,that are working today,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:31.43,Cap,,0,0,0,,and that can help you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.45,0:00:33.02,Cap,,0,0,0,,get hired, stand out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:33.86,Cap,,0,0,0,,and demonstrate your
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:34.40,Cap,,0,0,0,,value.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:35.93,Cap,,0,0,0,,Please register at the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:36.90,Cap,,0,0,0,,link in the post.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:37.83,Cap,,0,0,0,,See you then!
